
** Connection Problems

  - If more than one NIC exists then the *X-Server IP* Address should
    be specified. Go to xconfig, communication, xdmcp broadcast and
    add as user-defined ip xdmcp address the address of the X-Server
    in this case the PC-Address.

  - See also SystemEosNet.

  - On SuSE 9.0 look in the 'Editor for /etc/sysconfig' for the xdm
    entries. See also KdeKdm.
